title: Geetanjali 2
subTitle: Sreenu receives a directorial offer from Vishnu to shoot in a bungalow. Later, him and his crew realise that Vishnu orchestrated the ploy to seek revenge by trapping them in a haunted house.

title: Meri Ladaai
subTitle: An ambitious real estate agent falls in love with the sister of a powerful business tycoon. However, the girl's brother resents their relationship and tries to separate the lovers.

title: Sivudu
subTitle: A carefree young man's life is disrupted by rising crime in his locality and when his family faces danger, he decides to fight back.

title: Naagin Bani Suhaagan
subTitle: Vaishali, an ardent devotee of Lord Shiva, is blessed with a boon to transform herself into a shapeshifting snake. She falls into a dilemma when circumstances force her to go against her love.

title: Rakhwala No 1
subTitle: A man abducts his friend's girlfriend to unite the lovers but ends up kidnapping Pooja, the wrong girl. However, she heaves a sigh of relief upon escaping the clutches of her warring uncles.

title: Jallikattu
subTitle: A strong young man takes it upon himself to defeat a fierce bull and steal the bag of coins attached to its horns. His enemy wants him dead owing to his skills.

title: Aakhri Yudh
subTitle: Babji, a loan recovery agent, decides to help Kavya when he finds her being chased by her family. However, Kavya's brother thinks that Babji and her sister are lovers and attacks his family.

title: Hidimbha
subTitle: In Hyderabad, a series of murders targets young girls. Later, officers Aadhya and Abhay investigate as more victims disappear, soon discovering a common link among them.

title: DD Returns
subTitle: An event manager and his friends hide the money they stole in a haunted bungalow to evade the police but when they go back to retrieve it, the ghosts force them to play a dangerous game.

title: The Family Star
subTitle: Govardhan, a diligent architect, longs for a partner who understands his commitment to his large family. When Indu, a new tenant, moves in, his life starts to unfold in a new direction.

title: Naa Saami Ranga
subTitle: A man gains great notoriety in his village for his unmatched strength and brutal nature, which makes him a target of antisocial elements with a ruthless agenda.

title: Gambler No. 1
subTitle: Janaki agrees to marry her childhood friend Rummy, but not until he's become rich and powerful, so Rummy decides to become a gambler.

title: Gambler No. 1
subTitle: Janaki agrees to marry her childhood friend Rummy, but not until he's become rich and powerful, so Rummy decides to become a gambler.

title: Bunglow No 17
subTitle: Gautham and Deeksha, along with their daughter, move into an isolated bungalow gifted to them by Gautham's father. Soon, they start experiencing paranormal activities around the house.

title: The Real Shatru
subTitle: An encounter specialist faces a moral dilemma when he discovers that all his missions served the corupt politicians and businessmen, spurring him to seek redemption and justice.

title: Bhumi Rakshak
subTitle: Two half-brothers peacefully co-exist with each other and their families. However, the return of an old enemy threatens the unity of the close-knit family.

title: Kshatriya Ek Yodha
subTitle: An orphan pretends to love a girl in order to help his friend. However, he genuinely falls in love with her and tries to confess his feelings for her.

title: Manjulika Returns 2
subTitle: Four strangers across different walks of life serendipitously meet at a haunted graveyard. However, luck turns to misery when an insidious force awakens.

title: Bharaate
subTitle: Jagan, a local travel guide, falls in love with Radha, a tourist who visits his city. Though she leaves without saying goodbye, fate conspires to being them together again.

title: Alluri
subTitle: Iqbal, an aspiring police candidate, embarks on a journey to follow in the footsteps of Alluri, an upright officer, and discovers valuable lessons along the way.

title: Surya's Saturday
subTitle: A vigilante fights against injustice using his own unique moral code, where he only comes out to play on Saturdays.

title: The Return Of Lion
subTitle: When a social worker dies, his son must not only avenge his death but also prove his innocence when the welfare fund money accumulated by his family goes missing.

title: The Return Of Lion
subTitle: When a social worker dies, his son must not only avenge his death but also prove his innocence when the welfare fund money accumulated by his family goes missing.

title: Qatl Ka Raaz
subTitle: Kathir, an aspiring music director, meets Meera, a musician in a music shop and instantly falls for her. Later, things get absurd when he receives inappropriate pictures of her anonymously.

title: War On Terror Kandahar
subTitle: After a group of terrorists hijack a plane, an army major and the National Security Guard set off against all odds on a rescue mission.

title: Hanuman vs. Mahiravana
subTitle: Lord Hanuman goes to save Goddess Sita and defeat the king of Lanka, Ravana. To defend his kingdom, Ravana unleashes his most powerful ally, his brother, Mahiravana.

title: Intelligent
subTitle: DSP Ranjith Kalidoss battles both a serial killer and his own Parkinson's disease. However, his pursuit exposes a more elaborate and sinister scheme than he initially suspected.

title: Deewar Man of Power
subTitle: Childhood friends Bujji and Chitti decide to meet after 12 years. Bujji, a gangster, attempts to murder Sivanna, not knowing that he is Chitti's brother.

title: Jaguar
subTitle: Krishna, an orphan medical student, lives a seemingly ordinary life. However, unbeknownst to people, he is a vigilante named Jaguar who pursues a certain group of people in order to kill them.

title: Vijay Raghavan
subTitle: An honest IAS officer devotes his life to the upliftment of the youth in his locality. However, a corrupt businessman's ploy to poison these young minds compels him to challenge the criminal.

title: Indian Soldier Never On Holiday
subTitle: An army officer sets out to save the people of his country when he learns that an entire network of terrorists are operating in the city and are planning to carry out multiple terror attacks.

title: Ugram
subTitle: Shiva, a reckless CI officer, often lands himself in trouble. However, his impulsive actions take a dark turn when his family goes missing from a hospital after an accident.

title: Sangharsh Aur Vijay
subTitle: Badri is the protector of Badrinath temple. However, when a woman falls in love with him, his guru decides against making Badri his successor.

title: Munduvareda Adhyaya
subTitle: ACP Bala is in charge of investigating a prominent figure's mysterious murder. However, the mystery keeps getting even more complicated with each reveal instead of taking him closer to the criminal.
